H0.text: Seed is the phase in the life cycle of certain types of flowers that is most like the egg stage in the life cycle of a bird.

H1.text: Spore is the phase in the life cycle of certain types of flowers that is most like the egg stage in the life cycle of a bird.

H2.text: Pollen is the phase in the life cycle of certain types of flowers that is most like the egg stage in the life cycle of a bird.

H3.text: Immature flower is the phase in the life cycle of certain types of flowers that most resembles the egg stage in the life cycle of a bird.
